        <item>
          <actionDate>2015-02-09</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Permanent IRA Charitable Contribution Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>(Sec. 2) This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to make permanent the exclusion from gross income of distributions from individual retirement accounts made for charitable purposes. </p> <p>(Sec. 3) This provision exempts the budgetary effects of this Act from entry on PAYGO scorecards under the Statutory Pay-As-You-Go Act of 2010. </p>]]></text>
